@baseUrl = https://api.commerce.naver.com/external
@clientId = REPLACE_WITH_STORE_APP_ID
@timestamp = REPLACE_WITH_UNIX_TIMESTAMP_MS
@clientSecretSign = REPLACE_WITH_BASE64_BCRYPT_SIGNATURE
@accessToken = 31qjCKZ5aP2e31jsnluk8
@lastChangedFrom = 2025-01-01T00:00:00+09:00
@originalProductId = 12650488610
@dispatchDate = 2025-01-01T12:00:00+09:00

### Request SmartStore access token
# @name requestToken
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/oauth2/token
Content-Type: application/json
x-skip-auth: true

{
  "client_id": "{{clientId}}",
  "timestamp": {{timestamp}},
  "grant_type": "client_credentials",
  "client_secret_sign": "{{clientSecretSign}}",
  "type": "SELF"
}

### 최근 N분간 상태가 바뀐 주문 조회 (OrdersService.findLastChangedOrders)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/pay-order/seller/product-orders/last-changed-statuses?lastChangedFrom={{lastChangedFrom}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 주문 상세 조회 (OrdersService.getOrdersInfo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/pay-order/seller/product-orders/query
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "productOrderIds": [
    "2025120851603931"
  ]
}

### 주문 발송 처리 (OrdersService.postDeliveryProducts)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/pay-order/seller/product-orders/dispatch
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "dispatchProductOrders": [
    {
      "productOrderId": "PRODUCT_ORDER_ID_1",
      "deliveryMethod": "NOTHING",
      "deliveryCompanyCode": "",
      "trackingNumber": "",
      "dispatchDate": "{{dispatchDate}}"
    }
  ]
}

### 상품옵션정보조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/products/origin-products/12752749402
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

### 옵션/재고 업데이트 (StockService.updateOptionStock)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/v1/products/origin-products/{{originalProductId}}/option-stock
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

